        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Yeo Mi-Ran (Kim Ok-Vin) is a rookie attorney at Gilmu Law Firm, which works primarily with the entertainment industry. She is not interested in having a romantic relationship and she hates to lose to a man in anything.\n\nNam Gang-Ho (Yoo Teo) is a top actor in the entertainment industry. He is the most popular actor in South Korea due to his handsome appearance, intelligence, and kindness. He is sought after to work in romantic movies, but he doesn't actually trust women.\n\nYeo Mi-Ran and Nam Gang-Ho, who both don’t believe in love, fall into a love battle.",
